OL,3,C'Listen to local people' - calls for
OL,4,Chelp as village floods twice within
OL,5,Cweeks
OL,7,FResidents in a Somerset village are
OL,8,Ffacing further disruption as their
OL,9,Fhomes and businesses have for the
OL,10,Fsecond time in a matter of weeks.
OL,12,FCroscombe, near Wells, was affected by
OL,13,FStorm Henk in January and now
OL,14,Ffollowing heavy rainfall is once again
OL,15,Ffacing problems due to the water
OL,16,Fcoming through the valley.
OL,18,FPeter Graham is the Landlord of the
OL,19,FGeorge Inn.
