OL,3,C'Listen to local people' - calls for
OL,4,Chelp as village floods twice within
OL,5,Cweeks
OL,7,FHe said: "We went to bed around 1 am
OL,8,Fthinking we put our flood barrier out
OL,9,Fin the morning but at 5 am I was woken
OL,10,Fup by heavy banging and found out we
OL,11,Fwere flooded again."
OL,13,FCroscombe is in a valley where the
OL,14,Friver is narrow with low bridges that
OL,15,Fhave problems taking the water.
OL,17,FHe said the situation should be
OL,18,Fmanageable and is calling on
OL,19,Fgovernment support to help solve the
OL,20,Fproblems that have been identified in
OL,21,Fa previous report.
