OL,7,FPeter says "Unfortunately we've had
OL,8,Fsome practice getting back into
OL,9,Fbusiness after the flooding."
OL,11,FThe pub has waterproof flooring they
OL,12,Fcan hose and clean when the water
OL,13,Farrives but says the call to action is
OL,14,Fimportant to stop this from becoming a
OL,15,Fregular occurrence.
