OL,3,C'Listen to local people' - calls for
OL,4,Chelp as village floods twice within
OL,5,Cweeks
OL,7,FCouncillor Claire Sully has lived in
OL,8,Fthe village for more than 20 years.
OL,9,FShe says the flooding is happening
OL,10,Fevery few weeks now due to extreme
OL,11,Fweather that is becoming more
OL,12,Ffrequent. She says the local people
OL,13,Fhave to be listened to.
