OL,3,C'Listen to local people' - calls for
OL,4,Chelp as village floods twice within
OL,5,Cweeks
OL,7,FCllr Sully said: "Here we are again,
OL,8,FCroscombe has been flooded. The
OL,9,Fauthorities understand the issues and
OL,10,Fmore importantly, the local people
OL,11,Funderstand what needs to be done to
OL,12,Fprevent flooding like this. But we
OL,13,Fneed emergency funding in this village
OL,14,Fand areas around Shepton and wider
OL,15,FSomerset.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/8
