OL,3,C'Listen to local people' - calls for
OL,4,Chelp as village floods twice within
OL,5,Cweeks
OL,7,F"The local authority has to deliver
OL,8,Fthe work that needs to prevent it but
OL,9,Fthey can't do it if they don't have
OL,10,Fthe funding. So I'm calling on the
OL,11,Fgovernment to give emergency funding
OL,12,Fto areas like this. You will see the
OL,13,Fdevastation, these are people who are
OL,14,Fstill clearing up from the last flood
OL,15,Fin January. A few weeks later we now
OL,16,Fhave devastating flooding."
OL,18,FThere are calls for preventative
OL,19,Fmeasures to be sorted to stop people
OL,20,Ffrom seeing this happening to their
OL,21,Fhomes every few weeks.
