OL,4,Chelp as village floods twice within
OL,5,Cweeks
OL,7,FMeetings are taking place in the
OL,8,Fcoming weeks to respond to the issue.
OL,10,FA spokesperson for the Environment
OL,11,FAgency said: "Regarding Croscombe, we
OL,12,Fissued flood warnings in advance of
OL,13,Fthe flooding and have had operatives
OL,14,Fout before and since the flooding to
OL,15,Fensure trash screens and culverts were
OL,16,Fclear of debris.
OL,18,F"River levels in the area peaked early
OL,19,Fon Sunday morning with levels now
OL,20,Fdropping.
